    "text": "The \"Yandex Directory\" translation key is used to display the title of a Yandex folder. It appears in UI elements that interact with Yandex folders, such as buttons or dialog titles. Translators should ensure this text accurately reflects the meaning of \"Yandex Directory\".",
    "is_auto": true,
    "updated_at": "2025-05-20T09:46:31.687Z"
  },
